{"type":"message","id":"e8a0a79a","parentId":"812c6ab2","timestamp":"2026-04-21T01:27:53.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ktr9jidr05nc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# zry-project-v3\n\nThis template should help get you started developing with Vue 3 in Vite.\n\n## Recommended IDE Setup\n\n[VS Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/) + [Vue (Official)](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=Vue.volar) (and disable Vetur).\n\n## Recommended Browser Setup\n\n- Chromium-based browsers (Chrome, Edge, Brave, etc.):\n  - [Vue.js devtools](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/vuejs-devtools/nhdogjmejiglipccpnnnanhbledajbpd)\n  - [Turn on Custom Object Formatter in Chrome DevTools](http://bit.ly/object-formatters)\n- Firefox:\n  - [Vue.js devtools](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/vue-js-devtools/)\n  - [Turn on Custom Object Formatter in Firefox DevTools](https://fxdx.dev/firefox-devtools-custom-object-formatters/)\n\n## Customize configuration\n\nSee [Vite Configuration Reference](https://vite.dev/config/).\n\n## Project Setup\n\n```sh\nnpm install\n```\n\n### Compile and Hot-Reload for Development\n\n```sh\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compile and Minify for Production\n\n```sh\nnpm run build\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776734873822}}
{"type":"message","id":"b436348c","parentId":"e8a0a79a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T01:28:14.185Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create a comprehensive README.md based on what I know about the project - it's an education/career planning consulting platform with Vue 3 + Vite, with multiple service modules.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6w35nzhxzvwr_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# zry-project\n\n> 教育与职业规划咨询服务平台\n\n基于 **Vue 3 + Vite** 构建的移动优先 Web 应用，为青少年及职场人群提供测评、规划与咨询服务。\n\n---\n\n## 技术栈\n\n| 类别 | 技术 |\n|------|------|\n| 框架 | Vue 3 (Composition API) |\n| 构建 | Vite 8 |\n| 路由 | Vue Router 5 |\n| 状态 | Pinia (如已引入) |\n| 适配 | 移动端优先，响应式设计 |\n| IDE | VS Code + Vue Official 插件 |\n\n## 功能模块\n\n### 测评服务\n- 🔬 **天赋测评** — 指纹测试、多元智能评估、逻辑密码分析、艺术天赋识别\n- 🧠 **个性测评** — MBTI 职业性格测试、大五人格分析、霍兰德职业兴趣测试\n- 📊 **学业评估** — 学习习惯诊断、学科培优方案、升学路径规划、定制青少年学业规划\n- 💼 **职业规划** — 职业生命周期评估、新人职场适应、领导力与管理层培养\n\n### 内容中心\n- 📖 **徐博士说** — 专家专栏\n- 🎯 **案例解读** — 真实咨询案例分析\n- 🤝 **合作模式** — 服务合作方式介绍\n- 🏢 **公司介绍** — 企业背景与理念\n\n### 用户端\n- 👤 **个人中心** — 用户信息管理\n- 🔐 **登录注册** — 简单鉴权（localStorage）\n\n## 页面清单 (30+)\n\n```\n/                           首页\n/home/xu-bo-shi             徐博士说\n/home/an-li-jie-du          案例解读\n/home/he-zuo-mo-shi         合作模式\n/home/tian-fu-ce-shi        天赋测评\n/home/xue-ye-gui-hua        学业规划\n/home/zhi-ye-gui-hua        职业规划\n/home/xing-ge-ce-shi        性格测试\n/home/gong-si-jie-shao      公司介绍\n/home/good-child-guide      好孩子指南\n/service                   服务总览\n/service/hot/xing-qu-ban    兴趣班选择\n/service/hot/gong-zuo       工作探索\n/service/hot/xuan-ke        选科指导\n/service/personality/*      个性测评系列\n/service/study/*            学业规划系列\n/service/talent/*           天赋潜能系列\n/service/career/*           职业规划系列\n/profile                    个人中心\n/login                      登录页\n```\n\n## 开发\n\n```bash\n# 安装依赖\nnpm install\n\n# 开发模式 (热重载)\nnpm run dev\n\n# 生产构建\nnpm run build\n\n# 预览生产构建\nnpm run preview\n```\n\n## 移动端适配\n\n项目采用**移动端优先**设计，已完成部分页面适配（首页、App.vue 全局样式、指纹测试页），其余页面适配工作持续进行中。\n\n### 屏幕断点\n- 📱 **手机** ≤ 480px — 单列布局\n- 📱 **平板** 481px – 768px — 双列布局\n- 💻 **小桌面** 769px – 1024px — 三列布局\n- 🖥️ **大桌面** > 1024px — 多列布局，居中显示\n\n### 全局工具类\n`.container` `.card` `.btn` `.grid` `.flex` 等，详情见 `MOBILE_ADAPTER.md`。\n\n---\n\n## 项目结构\n\n```\nzry-project/\n├── index.html\n├── package.json\n├── vite.config.js\n├── jsconfig.json\n├── public/              静态资源\n├── src/\n│   ├── main.js          入口文件\n│   ├── App.vue          根组件\n│   ├── assets/          静态资源\n│   ├── components/      公共组件（如 BottomNav.vue）\n│   ├── router/\n│   │   └── index.js     路由配置\n│   ├── store/           状态管理\n│   └── views/           页面组件\n│       ├── Home.vue\n│       ├── Login.vue\n│       ├── Profile.vue\n│       ├── Service.vue\n│       ├── article/\n│       ├── home/\n│       └── service/\n│           ├── career/\n│           ├── hot/\n│           ├── personality/\n│           ├── study/\n│           └── talent/\n├── MOBILE_ADAPTER.md    移动端适配进度报告\n└── README.md\n```\n","path":"/Users/zhu/Desktop/zry_project_v1/zry-project/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-v2-aicodee-com","model":"MiniMax-M2.7-highspeed","usage":{"input":355,"output":1065,"cacheRead":18363,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19783,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776734873825,"responseId":"0636059a5b3f40a0d3232b8d0f48e096"}}
